ariation of cloud properties. This is likely\ndue to the estimated short lifetime of the clouds ($\\approx6$ Myr), which\nappears to be mainly regulated by cloud-cloud collision and/or shear processes.\nOverall, it thus seems that the presence of the large-scale bar and gas inflows\nto the centre of NGC 5806 affect cloud properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 17:19:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2023 11:56:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
