q} \\, T$ and $T$\nsatisfies a locally uniform estimate along ${\\mathcal B}$ implying decay of $T$\nto a unique tangent plane faster than a fixed exponential rate in the scale.\nThis result is central to the more refined analysis of $T$ we perform in\n\\cite{KrumWicb} and \\cite{KrumWicc}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 21:30:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-24"}
