indicator of its potency. If workload-allocator interplay in the\nvirtual address space suffices to evaluate a novel fragmentation definition,\nnumerous other useful applications of our tool can be studied. Both augmenting\n2DBP and exploring alternative computations on it provide ample fertile ground\nfor future research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2023 10:18:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2023 08:05:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
