 coefficients of\nthe spectral phase and reaching pulses similar to transform limited with\nfull-width at half-maximum (FWHM) of ca1.6 ps.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 22:15:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
